  "content": "<div class=\"content-main relative\">\n <h1 class=\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\">Video cứu người d&acirc;n bị sạt lở v&ugrave;i lấp</h1>\n <div class=\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [&amp;&gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n   <a href=\"/bao-phap-luat-tp-hcm-plo-p114.epi\" class=\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title=\"B&aacute;o Ph&aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\">\n    <figure class=\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style=\"width:55px;height:20px\" aria-label=\"Logo nh&agrave; xuất bản\">\n     <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n      <img src=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" alt=\"B&aacute;o Ph&aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\" width=\"176\" height=\"64\" />\n     </picture>\n    </figure></a>\n   <span><button class=\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"Theo d&otilde;i &quot;PLO&quot;\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n  <time datetime=\"2025-11-02T11:57:33.000Z\">7 giờ trước</time>\n  <a href=\"/sat-lo-t41477079.epi\" class=\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\">16\n   <!-- --> li&ecirc;n quan</a>\n  <a href=\"/video-cuu-nguoi-dan-bi-sat-lo-vui-lap-r53653281.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n  <i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-773px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"></i>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh, TP Đ&agrave; Nẵng phối hợp c&aacute;c lực lượng, người d&acirc;n cứu th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng một người bị sạt lở v&ugrave;i lấp.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <p class=\"text\">Ng&agrave;y 2-11, &ocirc;ng Lưu Huyền Thoại, Ph&oacute; Chủ tịch UBND x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh, <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/da-nang-tag11450.epi\">TP Đ&agrave; Nẵng</a>, x&aacute;c nhận tr&ecirc;n địa b&agrave;n vừa xảy ra vụ sạt lở đất nghi&ecirc;m trọng.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Th&ocirc;ng tin ban đầu cho hay, khoảng 14 giờ c&ugrave;ng ng&agrave;y, vụ <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/sat-lo-tag4528.epi\">sạt lở</a> đất xảy ra tại th&ocirc;n 4, x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh, v&ugrave;i lấp s&aacute;u căn nh&agrave; v&agrave; một người d&acirc;n.</p>\n  <div class=\"video-wrapper max-h-[80vh]\" style=\"width:625px;height:360px;background:url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/player-default-03.png) no-repeat center center;background-size:cover\"></div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> C&aacute;c lực lượng cứu hộ cứu người d&acirc;n bị sạt lở v&ugrave;i lấp. Clip: AT </em></p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Tiếp nhận th&ocirc;ng tin, c&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; phối hợp c&aacute;c lực lượng, người d&acirc;n tổ chức cứu nạn khẩn cấp.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Đến khoảng 15 giờ 30, lực lượng <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/cuu-ho-tag12828.epi\">cứu hộ</a> đ&atilde; đưa được nạn nh&acirc;n ra ngo&agrave;i, đến trạm y tế x&atilde; cấp cứu.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:359px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" May mắn nạn nh&acirc;n chỉ bị thương nhẹ \" width=\"625\" height=\"359\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> May mắn nạn nh&acirc;n chỉ bị thương nhẹ </em></p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Qua kh&aacute;m sơ bộ, c&aacute;c y b&aacute;c sĩ x&aacute;c định nạn nh&acirc;n chỉ bị thương nhẹ, tinh thần ổn định.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh v&agrave; c&aacute;c lực lượng đang vận động sơ t&aacute;n 20 hộ với 60 người tại khu vực n&agrave;y về nơi an to&agrave;n.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:833px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"833\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:468px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" C&aacute;c lực lượng nỗ lực cứu người d&acirc;n bị sạt lở v&ugrave;i lấp ra ngo&agrave;i. \" width=\"625\" height=\"468\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> C&aacute;c lực lượng nỗ lực cứu người d&acirc;n bị sạt lở v&ugrave;i lấp ra ngo&agrave;i. </em></p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Đến nay, x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh vẫn c&ograve;n bị c&ocirc; lập từ trận lũ lịch sử vừa qua.</p>\n  <p class=\"text body-author text-right\"><strong>THANH NHẬT</strong></p>\n </div>\n <div class=\"pswp\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  <div class=\"pswp__bg\"></div>\n  <div class=\"pswp__scroll-wrap\">\n   <div class=\"pswp__container\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__top-bar\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__counter\"></div>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title=\"Close (Esc)\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title=\"Share\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title=\"Toggle fullscreen\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title=\"Zoom in/out\